{"tid":347033,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"比利祝福尼馬：我都好鐘意巴黎","createTime":"2017-08-04T12:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T21:39:24.000Z","uid":31208,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0387d497945811abfa23f22b79d2cd9f1321605","tid":347033,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T12:37:17.000Z","msg":"比利祝福尼馬：我都好鐘意巴黎<br />\n<br />\n新浪網 2017-08-04 12:16:43  <br />\n<br />\n　　在尼馬完成加盟巴黎聖日耳門的轉會後，球王比利在Twitter上向他表示了祝賀。<br />\n　　球王比利是世界球壇最偉大的球員之一，而尼馬和他一樣，都出自於山度士青訓。尼馬也是現任巴西國家隊10號球衣的所有者，而比利則是巴西國家隊歷史上最為偉大的10號球星。<br />\n　　在尼馬正式加盟巴黎聖日耳門的消息傳來之後，比利在Twitter上向尼馬表示了祝賀。比利配了一幅自己在埃菲爾鐵塔下手捧列美特金盃的圖片，他寫道：「恭喜你，尼馬。祝你在新的挑戰中一切好運，巴黎是一個美麗的城市，它也是我全世界最喜愛的地方之一！」"},{"pid":"28064041d7bdf9c67d917bc83757ee15ec536079","tid":347033,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T12:41:43.000Z","msg":"有時真係寧願比利好早就死左 上神枱做傳奇<br />\n都好過依家成日出來鳩up既活著傳奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee5b874cf23141b7a8c92f5c2a4082a6348a3f4","tid":347033,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T12:43:13.000Z","msg":"係咪想做人老豆呀<br />\n日撚日吹奏尼馬"},{"pid":"d83cb04242a9730c19184b6b7f140b8071999478","tid":347033,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T12:45:05.000Z","msg":"我比面叫你一聲比利哥，唔好再吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da53626eb68d7405f49e93a9d16e3540b564fe50","tid":347033,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T12:45:58.000Z","msg":"行行開少少喇老坑 又唔係唔知把口臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca031c151599368fc6edca19f336d35d6c614a7","tid":347033,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T12:46:25.000Z","msg":"詛咒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373ab8be3b3a003c643922656a9029c0f197ad76","tid":347033,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T12:48:36.000Z","msg":"尼馬會唔會斷腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3540a20c426afc7210f60b48494841c02adf001","tid":347033,"uid":33443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T12:50:27.000Z","msg":"巴黎是一個美麗的城市<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b1e6d53ebf2bef482edbfca55d79382856c026","tid":347033,"uid":17166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T21:39:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴黎是一個美麗的城市<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n短期內唔好去巴黎旅行<br />\n特別巴黎鐵塔附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}